  "prob_desc_notes": "NoteIn the first example the desired positions might be 6 and 8 or 7 and 8. Positions 6 and 7 contain letters 'a', position 8 contains letter 'b'. The pair of positions 1 and 8 is not suitable because there is an uppercase letter 'B' between these position.In the second example desired positions can be 7, 8 and 11. There are other ways to choose pretty set consisting of three elements.In the third example the given string s does not contain any lowercase letters, so the answer is 0.",
